<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1">

	<title>채팅방 조회</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"> <!-- load bootstrap css -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css"> <!-- load fontawesome -->

	<style>
		.divchat{
			width: 1200px;
			height: 400px;
			border: 1px solid #ccc;
			overflow-y: auto;
		}
		body        { padding-top:80px; }
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div>
			<h2>
				채팅방 조회
			</h2>
			<p>채팅방 ID값을 입력하면 전체 채팅이 조회 됩니다</p>
			<br><br>
			<form action="/admin_getchat" method="post">
				<label>채팅방 ID</label>
				<input type="number" name="thread_id" value="<%=chatdata&&chatdata[0]?chatdata[0].super_thread_id:null%>"/>
				<input type="submit" value="채팅 검색"/>
			</form>
			<br><br>
			<p>메세지ID, 유저 ID, 보낸시간, 내용</p>
			<div class="divchat">
				<%if(chatdata){
					for(var i=0;i<chatdata.length;i++){
					    %>
				<%=chatdata[i].message_id_unique%>
				<%=chatdata[i].sending_user_id%>
				<%=chatdata[i].send_date%>
				<%=chatdata[i].type=="text"?chatdata[i].body:""%>
				<image src="<%=chatdata[i].type=="image"?chatdata[i].body:""%>"></image>
				<br>
					<%}
				}%>
			</div>
			<br><br><br><a href="/">관리자 홈으로</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>